title: 'Very Good Quality Pen Drive for the price'
body: *Important* - Not sure why they sell it as 3.0 maybe not to eat into their 3.2 drives sales. but this is USB 3.2 Gen 1. While connecting to my pc it shows as 3.2.  The Speed is good, The write speed is 46 Mbps and above. while transferring small size files it will surely come down, I transferred 1.5 - 2 GB Movies. For that its very good. Read speed I'm sure its around 100 Mbps.  Not much of heating issue. I am using with my LG TV, works perfectly.
